Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is how you do swings!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:32.64,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:52.82,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That dream made me nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:54.57,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:56.92,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna looked cool,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:58.93,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,even on a swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:02.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:05.08,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What, you don't need to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:09.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato may have made enough for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:10.37,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:11.88,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:13.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:15.47,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:19.97,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Something, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:55.77,Title1,Sign 0252,0000,0000,0000,,My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:53.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:57.90,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, where's Sunakawa-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:59.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He said he had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.00,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:02.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I only asked because you guys are always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:05.78,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:08.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'll have some leftovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:10.16,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so give them to him later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.55,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember these!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:14.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're "cake the kele," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:16.59,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Almost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,They're cake salé.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:21.30,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I made some star-shaped ones, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.17,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,They bring back happy memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.31,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,When's your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:33.82,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,January 1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:34.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:36.44,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's right in the middle of winter break,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:41.78,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 0338,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! \NThanks! \NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:41.78,SFX-BlackWhite,SIgn 0338,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo!  \N\NHappy New Year!  \N\NHappy Birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:41.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,but my friends always came all the way \Nto our door to wish me "happy birthday."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:45.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,January 1st, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:47.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to start making preparations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:50.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's Day, so there's mochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:54.58,SFX-BlueWhite,Sign 0350,0000,0000,0000,,Mochi Cream Puffs   {\c&H7338AB&}Mochi Waffles   {\c&H1CB6D4&}Mochi Donuts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:52.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,There are mochi sweets, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:54.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which ones would be good...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.59,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,When is your birthday, Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:57.31,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:03.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, June 15th.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:04.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.55,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,June 15th...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.65,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's real soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:18.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, it is, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:21.03,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0418,0000,0000,0000,,OMG, I really said it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:18.96,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:21.03,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I made it sound like \NI want you to celebrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.33,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:23.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:24.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:25.59,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:26.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:31.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't need anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:33.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,On that day, can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:41.30,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have you stay with me the whole day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:02.88,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:06.45,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,thank you for being born into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.78,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,People are born into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:12.66,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.17,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:15.41,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.62,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, yours is on January 1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:20.17,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You have great memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.17,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0520,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(107,1)}Well, given the date...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:23.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I remember your birthday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's September 13th, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I remember, every year
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:29.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,in elementary school, I was invited \Nto your birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:30.64,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So, whose birthday is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.37,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato's!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:35.67,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yamato-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:36.59,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,June 15th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:40.61,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The 15th...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:42.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:45.25,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You have something on the 15th?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:47.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.29,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:50.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What're you going to do for her birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.34,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.01,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:57.08,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato said she doesn't want anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,She just
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:01.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,wants me to spend time with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:03.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,She said that's all she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:05.18,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:10.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to take her to a \Nlot of places and celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:11.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You would.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Brainstorm with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:14.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:17.23,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0615,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(249,1)\an8\fs24}Thank You
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:17.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:21.73,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:24.73,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,People are born into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:29.24,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Take, you're going to become \Na big brother in January.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.60,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you push that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:36.96,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:41.07,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Forty, but I'm told my physical age is twenty-two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:42.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,So young...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.67,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't carry anything heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:47.42,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:48.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:49.84,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:52.22,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,When I had you, \NI had to carry another pregnant lady
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:55.94,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,to the delivery room, \Nwhen she went into labor first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.56,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,But I was fine then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:57.56,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0657,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(105,1)\an7}Press that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:06:59.43,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:00.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,but that's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:03.98,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.94,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:11.29,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have a little brother or sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.66,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,People are born into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.66,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0714,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(129,1)}Get out already
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:18.79,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're going to become \Na big brother, Takeo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:19.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.79,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know whether it's a boy or a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:25.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And your mom is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:26.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Forty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:27.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:31.09,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun as a big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.56,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:35.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you'd be a great father, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:39.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'll be a great mother, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:42.81,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0741,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}*blush*
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:44.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:46.07,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.30,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I have something \NI need to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.87,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wondering if Suna's been \Nacting a bit strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:58.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But he seems like his usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:04.58,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read Suna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:09.30,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,He almost never talks about himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.96,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, could it be that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.72,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He's been hanging out with you all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but now he spends less time \Nwith you. He might be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:24.73,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Sunakawa-kun adores you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:29.23,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, we don't have to spend \Nmy birthday by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.37,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Let's invite Sunakawa-kun, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:32.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:34.99,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.16,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.49,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.04,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:54.38,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come and celebrate Yamato's \Nbirthday with us on the 15th?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:54.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:55.68,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:59.01,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato thought you might feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.56,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:08.40,SFX-BlackWhite,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(275,1)\an8}Stare
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.13,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:08.40,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I have something on the 15th.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:09.97,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.78,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,So it isn't that he's feeling lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.78,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why did that even come up, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:18.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought you've been acting \Na little different lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:21.08,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I just wondered if something was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.04,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:28.04,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there is something going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:32.35,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,if he doesn't want to talk about it, \NI'm not going to force him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:36.30,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait till he chooses to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:42.95,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So, about this schedule you put together \Nfor Yamato-san's birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:43.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:47.94,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,This schedule is packed like a day \Nin the life of a US president.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What? Tell me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:58.32,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0951,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}6 AM: Watch sunrise at Enoshima  \N7 AM: Beach walk ~ gather seashells, etc.  \N8 AM: Movie ~look up what's in cinemas \N10 AM: Amusement park  \N12 PM: Lunch ~somewhere good \N1 PM: Zoo  \N2 PM: Hiking  \N3 PM: Tea in a café  \N4 PM: Park  \N5 PM: Back to Enoshima to watch sunset  \N6 PM: Walk her home
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.53,Default - margin,S,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, the 6 AM thing has to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.01,Default - margin,S,0000,0000,0000,,This plan assumes sunshine,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:56.48,Default - margin,S,0000,0000,0000,,but what will you do if it rains?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:58.32,Default - margin,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:02.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,There's also no time for breaks and for \Ngetting from point A to point B.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:05.74,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Probably, no one except you could \Nhandle this kind of schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:06.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.21,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I need to start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:11.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What are some places you can go, \Neven when it's raining?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:17.09,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,How about that place we went after the school \Nfestival when we were in junior high?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:20.73,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It was some indoor place where you could \Nbowl and do karaoke and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:22.35,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:23.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,When we went, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:30.99,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:33.88,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't fit your fingers into the bowling ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.82,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 1035,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(231,1)\an8}Hilarious...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:35.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,so you just grabbed them to throw them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:40.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:43.02,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Every time it was your turn, \Nthe whole bowling alley was staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:45.27,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Toward the end, you'd attracted a small crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:47.68,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:50.46,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1047,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(224,1)\an8}It was like you were playing softball
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:50.46,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Who could forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.71,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1051,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}6 AM: Bowling  \N7 AM  \N8 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.08,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't open at 6 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.12,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They open at 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:56.96,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, 10 it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what to do for lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:11:00.97,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1058,0000,0000,0000,,10 AM: Bowling  \N12 PM: Lunch
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:00.18,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Beef bowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:00.97,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:04.12,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it better to pick a place \Nwith a good dessert selection?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.84,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato-san likes baking,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:08.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,so she probably likes seeing and eating sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:10.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:11.21,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's her birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:13.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd like to let her eat something amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:15.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,How about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:17.27,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It appears they take reservations,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:18.99,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,and their menu looks pretty extensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:20.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.16,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making a reservation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:24.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.67,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's left?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.31,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Aquariums,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,planetariums,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,the movies...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:31.94,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You had that one down, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.04,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's about it, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,A planetarium, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:37.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,In elementary school, we went to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:40.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,When we went,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:42.80,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,you got stuck in a hole they were trying to repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.44,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You managed to get out on your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:48.31,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,but they thought you were \Nsome underground monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You have a really good memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:53.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.25,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,A planetarium, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:58.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato likes stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:58.82,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,so this'll make her happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:00.22,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to be good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:04.95,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're really into it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It'll be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:11.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew it was so fun to celebrate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:13.21,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,the birthday of someone you care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.66,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:17.80,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.59,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:23.22,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're all places I've been to with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, given that we've been friends for ten years...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:29.60,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's right... We've been \Nfriends a really long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.92,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What about her birthday present, by the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:32.75,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'd totally forgotten about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:39.21,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you need presents for birthdays!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:40.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:40.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have money?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:41.45,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.24,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1241,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Well, with how often you eat Korean BBQ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.24,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to lend you some?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:45.29,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,How can I use someone else's money \Nto celebrate Yamato's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:46.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a part-time job, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.65,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:51.25,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1251,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(159,1)\an7}Anything goes, as long as \Nit has good hourly pay and \Nis OK hiring short-term, \Nhigh school students!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:49.61,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get a part-time job!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.25,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:54.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:54.58,SFX-Red,Sign 1254,0000,0000,0000,,Zing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:13:00.88,SFX-BlueWhite,Sign 1258,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}10 AM: Meet in front of station  \N12 PM: Lunch  \N2 PM: Park if sunny, café if rain  \N3 PM:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:00.88,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's done all the research.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:07.17,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.68,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one lucky guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:13.99,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure my day with Yamato is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.98,EyecatchA,Sign 1315,0000,0000,0000,,Morning
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.98,EyecatchB,Sign 1317,0000,0000,0000,,Afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.73,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you heading somewhere again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:23.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I have to stop by somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:25.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll just go home after that and crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:26.49,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.16,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.49,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:36.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:38.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:40.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Something... I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:42.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:43.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:48.57,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,If he's fine, it's all good...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:54.61,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So Sunakawa-kun \Nwasn't lonely, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.64,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1354,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(278,1)\an8}That's good
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:56.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's celebrate your birthday just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:57.23,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1355,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's good        It sure is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.23,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:13:59.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just one more week!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:02.44,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay that I feel so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.65,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,So happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go to a job interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:10.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A job?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you look forward to your birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:15.19,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But I really don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:18.55,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy enough spending time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:20.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying, it's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:21.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:24.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let me do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:25.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:30.30,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:33.56,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1432,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}As of June 8th  \NGouda Takeo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:31.94,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:33.56,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one lucky guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like for this to be short-term.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.81,Default,Store,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're a rare find,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:41.69,Default,Store,0000,0000,0000,,so we'd love to have you longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:42.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:45.07,SignB,Sign 1443,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thanks! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:43.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:45.07,Default,Store,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:45.93,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:47.59,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I have a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:48.70,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.45,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.45,SignB,Sign 1451,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}Bro Café \N\N{\c&H251CBE&\fs26}Machos \N\N{\c&H92D8CD&\fs18}Manager: Susie Honeyama
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:52.45,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:55.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The menu's short, so I should \Nbe able to memorize it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:58.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't what I mean, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.71,SFX-RedBlack,Sign 1459,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(191,1)}Well, whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Come with Yamato next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:03.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You told Yamato-san that you're getting a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:06.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were keeping everything a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:17.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:21.27,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:25.09,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Can you help me choose her present?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:26.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:31.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered what you \Nused to pick as gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What did I give you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:35.99,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Bugs... And rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.00,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,How about this, Takeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? A bowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:45.75,SignC,Sign 1542,0000,0000,0000,,Café au lait bowl and tea spoon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:45.75,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Last time, Yamato-san was talking about how \Ncute a café au lait bowl was, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.47,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:49.33,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:51.76,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like one to drink café au lait from!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:56.01,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a café au lait bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:58.27,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1557,0000,0000,0000,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:58.27,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,In your hand, it looks more like a teacup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:03.56,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna's very observant of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:06.02,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,He always keeps an eye out for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:10.40,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, how about that for Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:15.41,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that look cute on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to get this for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:21.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:24.95,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hate for it to sell out before I get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:26.39,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see if they can put it on hold for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.30,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1628,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.30,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They said it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.42,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:33.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:37.81,SignB,Sign 1636,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Bro Café  \N\N{\fs24\c&HA7B0DF&}Machos
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.81,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're looking forward to this, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.49,Default,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:47.84,Default,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,Are you new?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:48.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:51.99,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Protein teas, right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.23,Default,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, which gym do you go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:56.18,Default,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,You have wonderful delts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:57.74,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one lucky guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:57.74,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I just have 'em naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:16:59.99,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.76,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:06.04,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1704,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}Welcome back
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:06.04,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,You ask the same questions as your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:09.56,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:11.83,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,but I saw Makoto-kun at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:12.55,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:15.05,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,I heard his father's been hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.89,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:20.74,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:23.04,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't the type to tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:26.27,Sunakawa,Sign 1724,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1431,1)\fs20}Sunakawa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:30.59,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:31.78,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:40.18,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mom's gone overseas with Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:43.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reach them on their cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.92,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Did your mom say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:54.66,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,He collapsed the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:55.92,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,so he's kind of in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:58.04,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's not "kind of"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:00.26,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to need surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:03.68,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But I've asked my uncle to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.74,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,When is the surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:09.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,June 15th.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:15.19,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, June 15th...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:20.45,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, people are born into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:22.45,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,And people are taken from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.45,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:28.41,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you to the surgery, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:31.84,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What about Yamato-san's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:32.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:33.46,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:37.33,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain what's going on to Yamato, \Nand she'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell Yamato-san about my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:45.10,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She'll take it too seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:47.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato will understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:49.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Takeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:54.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get in the way of my friend \Nspending his first girlfriend's birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:55.36,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.36,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you looking forward to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.36,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't getting in the way of anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:01.12,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:05.62,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:11.84,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you scrap the birthday plan you've been \Nlooking forward to, and come to the surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:14.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,it won't make me feel any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:19.52,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's situation isn't anything new.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.62,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I've been kind of prepared for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:25.79,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:29.25,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna's father
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:31.40,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,is a kind person who never \Nleft much of an impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:34.40,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't letting anyone see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:38.09,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,He's always had heart problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:41.16,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,He collapsed once before...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:43.07,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe when you were in elementary school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:46.48,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, they weren't sure he'd make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:53.74,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,So Mom never said anything to me, \Neven though she knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:55.05,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's a real grown-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:59.33,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,There are things I don't know about Suna,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.89,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,even though I've known him more than ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.50,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I know his birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:08.17,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,and what kind of underwear he wears,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:11.10,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,there's still a lot I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:14.77,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,A lot... But Suna...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:19.62,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,There is a lot I do know, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:25.12,SignD,Sign 2022,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14}Bro Café
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.69,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:30.00,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 2030,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(188,1)\an7}What's with that getup?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:30.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you headed to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:32.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:36.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, I'm going to respect your wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:39.88,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't need to worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:49.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That does make me feel a bit better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:55.67,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:56.72,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:59.09,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:03.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:05.53,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:11.66,Phone,Sign 2110,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Received Messages \N\NFrom: Yamato Rinko \NSubject: I'm hyped! \N\NTakeo-kun, thank you for planning tomorrow! \NI'm so excited, I can't sleep!  \NI'm too worked up!  Too happy!  \NThanks, Takeo-kun!  \NI'm one lucky girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.92,Phone,Sign 2115,0000,0000,0000,,Compose Message  \N\NSee you tomorrow, in front of the station, at 10 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:21.92,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:27.03,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to spend a good birthday with Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:32.62,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to give it everything I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:51.05,Title2,Sign 2248,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(1,473)}My Friend and I
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:49.03,Default - margin,S,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: My Friend and I.
